"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Kenneth Law admitted to charges related to victims in Canada. However, families believe he should also face charges in the UK for 79 deaths in Britain.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kenneth Law Charges\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kenneth Law dijo que hizo cosas malas en Canada. Pero las familias piensan que tambien debe tener problemas en el Reino Unido por 79 muertes en Gran Bretana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cargos de Kenneth Law\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Romania says a Russian drone was likely hit over Ukraine by air defenses, which changed its path.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Drone Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rumania dice que un dron ruso fue golpeado sobre Ucrania por defensas aereas, lo que cambio su camino.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Dron Ruso\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The explosion of a Blue Origin rocket is a setback for the company and NASA's plans for the Moon.\",            \"english_title\": \"Blue Origin Rocket Explosion\",            \"translated_version\": \"La explosion de un cohete de Blue Origin es un problema para la compania y los planes de la NASA para la Luna.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosion de Cohete Blue Origin\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Sixteen students died in a fire that swept through a dormitory while they were sleeping.\",            \"english_title\": \"Dormitory Fire Tragedy\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dieciseis estudiantes murieron en un incendio que paso por un dormitorio mientras dormian.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tragedia de Incendio en Dormitorio\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Shi Yongxin was sentenced to 24 years in prison for stealing money and taking bribes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Shi Yongxin Sentenced\",       